node.text: So proud of @bransonsam – he’s released some brilliant songs as @wavesrushin and is really finding his voice as a musician. When I heard the first song he released – Colours Fade - I wondered if he would ever be able to top it. Then came Let It Bruise, a poignant song about mental health and allowing yourself to be vulnerable. Don’t Be So Hard on Yourself, brought tears to my eyes. I loved hearing Bellie, Sam’s wonderful wife, collaborate with him on this moving song about togetherness and overcoming. It’s an important reminder to be gentle with yourself, even when things around you may not quite be going your way. Cold Nights is his latest song, which is so full of emotion. You can listen to the full EP now. #wavesrushin
